net.sf.mmm.util.metakey.api

Interface MetakeyMultimedia

  • All Superinterfaces:
    MetakeyCore
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    MetakeyAudioVideo, MetakeyGraphics, MetakeyId3v2, MetakeyMovie, MetakeyMusic

    public interface MetakeyMultimedia
extends MetakeyCore
    This interface is a collection of constants defining keys for metadata-properties of multimedia content.
    Author:
    Joerg Hohwiller (hohwille at users.sourceforge.net)

    • Field Detail

      • GENRE

        static final String GENRE
        The genre of the audio/video content. E.g. "Blues" or "Thriller".
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • PRODUCER

        static final String PRODUCER
        The name of the producer(s) of the audio/video content.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • PUBLISHER

        static final String PUBLISHER
        The name of the publisher, label or company that published the content.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • MEDIA

        static final String MEDIA
        The number of the media if the content belongs to a whole that is divided into several media (e.g. several CDs, DVDs or BRs). It is the number of the media that contains the content and may be followed by a slash and the maximum number of medias (e.g. "1/2").
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • TRACK

        static final String TRACK
        The track-number of the content (e.g. index on a CD).
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values
